@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>We value your privacy. This policy explains the types of personal data we collect, how we use it, and your rights over your information.</p>

    <h2>What Data We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li><strong>Personal Details:</strong> When you sign up for an event or contact us, we may gather your name, email, and other contact information.</li>
        <li><strong>Website Usage Information:</strong> We track how you interact with our site, including your IP address, browser details, and pages viewed.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>We use the data we collect to:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>Manage event registrations and your account.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about events and your registrations.</li>
        <li>Improve our website and services.</li>
        <li>Send updates and promotional content if you’ve opted to receive them.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your personal data is retained only for as long as needed to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. Once it's no longer necessary, we securely erase or anonymize your information.</p>

    <h2>Your Data Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>Access to the data we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Requesting corrections to any incorrect data.</li>
        <li>Requesting the deletion of your data.</li>
        <li>Withdrawing your consent to data processing at any time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Policy Updates</h2>
    <p>We may revise this policy periodically. Any changes will be posted on this page. We recommend reviewing the policy regularly for any updates.</p>

    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions regarding this policy, please reach out to us:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a></li>
        <li>Phone: (123) 456-7890</li>
    </ul>
</div>
